{"tid":1071309,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【颱風山竹】塌樹阻路擋不住「山竹BB」　救護員首在救護車上接生","createTime":"2019-03-21T09:10:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-24T11:59:57.000Z","uid":2748,"like":58,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"af56256e3cf46c64b02a932c51a632745c263e74","tid":1071309,"uid":2748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T09:10:25.000Z","msg":"去年9月16日超強颱風「山竹」襲港，街上滿佈塌樹，到處都是前無去路的畫面。但救急扶危的救護員，在收到求救後總得想辦法出動去救人，署理救護隊目梁志樂和同伴，在山竹襲港當天，他們竟遇到有孕婦需送院分娩，就是「山竹BB」的母親王小姐。<br />\n<br />\n當日塌樹情況較嚴重，救護車被擋在路上無法回醫院，於是召來另一輛救護車過車。王小姐上了車後，作動更甚，嬰兒要出世了。入職7年的梁志樂育有兩名女兒，亦曾到產房陪伴大太分娩，但在救護車內為孕婦分娩卻是第一次，「我都第一次係車度做緊急分娩手術，好緊張。」鏡頭前井井有條回答問題，梁志樂鏡頭後卻禁不住興奮追問記者，「係咪有山竹（女嬰花名）嘅相睇？」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2459646/org/3f61ee79f2465f0385c2d2040afa146f.jpg/pc8S7MexpkGxVP8_nU2xP7SJ3J5-yzsyWkZlg1pGZYM?v=w1600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2459646%2Forg%2F3f61ee79f2465f0385c2d2040afa146f.jpg%2Fpc8S7MexpkGxVP8_nU2xP7SJ3J5-yzsyWkZlg1pGZYM%3Fv%3Dw1600&h=7d2a221a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n王小姐在山竹襲港期間驚險誕女，因此把女兒花名叫山竹。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2459652/org/4c4e2e6e09d5db641c24894234ebff67.jpg/nPEEXIwTXVqR1ndmi0Xn3CRPyotpTBcCv1yppr9cqaY?v=w1600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2459652%2Forg%2F4c4e2e6e09d5db641c24894234ebff67.jpg%2FnPEEXIwTXVqR1ndmi0Xn3CRPyotpTBcCv1yppr9cqaY%3Fv%3Dw1600&h=bc9e1189&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n三名救護員憶述，當日路上塌樹阻礙救護車前往孕婦家中。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2459618/org/87ea1a42a3ebd47428394769b6262c97.jpg/jc3PF2pqz_UezlbrUJGyqgCAZkoHsntUuVidc7lYnXM\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2459618%2Forg%2F87ea1a42a3ebd47428394769b6262c97.jpg%2Fjc3PF2pqz_UezlbrUJGyqgCAZkoHsntUuVidc7lYnXM&h=de521d56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2459617/org/797ff88d4d5e7322a0fec603c99397d3.jpg/UtUvtW-WQEbvect6GfZjKmBQ7VnYDGaGtnz-xLZ8_sQ\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2459617%2Forg%2F797ff88d4d5e7322a0fec603c99397d3.jpg%2FUtUvtW-WQEbvect6GfZjKmBQ7VnYDGaGtnz-xLZ8_sQ&h=5c7b2637&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n救護車被困在青山公路<br />\n<br />\n見到王小姐後，發現她的陣痛頻密度約2至3分鐘一次，梁志樂形容情況算危急，知道快要生產了，「BB就快出嚟！」唯一那條路，居然亦有塌樹，「救護車被大樹完全困死喺青山公路入面。」梁志樂見到遠方有消防員，吩咐救護員吳瑞洪向他們求助。<br />\n<br />\n吳瑞洪指，無奈情況太惡劣，「棵樹真係太粗壯，真係清唔到，事後先知，前方仲恐怖，塌咗燈柱。」救護員羅翰勤指，他們向通訊中心求助，最終派來另一輛救護車，在另一端協助。<br />\n<br />\n在風雨交加的情況下，眾人等待另一輛救護車增援，王小姐出現「着冠」，必須即時為她接生。三名救護員雖然已接受訓練，但均是首次為孕婦接生。僅24歲的吳瑞洪憶述當日情況，「真正見到一個新生命誕生，始終難免會緊張少少，摸上手有血有淚。」<br />\n<br />\n即使已為兩女之父的梁志樂亦坦言很緊張，「出生前始終變數好大，一嚟自己第一次接生，腦入面都有好多自己要做嘅決定同處理方法。當BB成功出世，檢查完維生指數後，真係鬆一口氣。」<br />\n<br />\n女嬰身上有一塊樹葉 原因是......<br />\n<br />\n最終母女平安，女嬰的花名為「山竹」，現時已經逾5個月大。當日女嬰送到北區醫院急症室後，北區醫院急症室醫生黃志強指，女嬰身上有一塊樹葉，猶如「風之女」。<br />\n<br />\n三名救護員便笑指，「應該包實晒嫁喎，唔知塊葉係唔係黐住喺我哋身上！」每日面對眾多令救護員黯然的情況，一個新生命誕生相對可為他們帶來喜悅。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2459657/org/515824f722a7265aa88af949da4b57ce.jpg/5il2SYnK-Cc6d1yl01DZd1ngbL9j1LF-xiJoEcYiaBE\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2459657%2Forg%2F515824f722a7265aa88af949da4b57ce.jpg%2F5il2SYnK-Cc6d1yl01DZd1ngbL9j1LF-xiJoEcYiaBE&h=aefeb4a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2459656/org/666f650d3aacd49f8c5605d5b6d55f7f.jpg/1DhFJyYtt2wFKFmibpASm20pAqB-aapwAOxBKQDsQSk\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2459656%2Forg%2F666f650d3aacd49f8c5605d5b6d55f7f.jpg%2F1DhFJyYtt2wFKFmibpASm20pAqB-aapwAOxBKQDsQSk&h=fe57a1e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2554081/org/33d5e859c9ac7595a3adc28d2c9a8147.JPG/ts2g6l0yJWG59pvO3kXCfwbc57d0H0O0fpC_aVuQv2k?v=w1600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2554081%2Forg%2F33d5e859c9ac7595a3adc28d2c9a8147.JPG%2Fts2g6l0yJWG59pvO3kXCfwbc57d0H0O0fpC_aVuQv2k%3Fv%3Dw1600&h=83ee74af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（左起）署理救護隊目梁志樂、署理救護監督(新界東北)鄭德誠 、署理助理救護總長(新界北)王律文、 上水救護站主管梁文浩、救護員羅翰勤、救護員吳瑞洪，一齊參與接「山竹」出世。"},{"pid":"557d86b8c67de194fabf550d60bcd06bda6accbd","tid":1071309,"uid":2748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T12:45:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86353decb3ca00ad3aae92e7afea413dfbceb9a3","tid":1071309,"uid":2748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T05:08:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a19b6d8a678eff9eb23fb95b1c53c9845e6e8042","tid":1071309,"uid":2404,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T05:43:34.000Z","msg":"唔怕生壞命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb700a17c259e476aceb854350d053abca5b3bbd","tid":1071309,"uid":47208,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"a19b6d8a678eff9eb23fb95b1c53c9845e6e8042","tid":1071309,"uid":2404,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T05:43:34.000Z","msg":"唔怕生壞命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T10:52:34.000Z","msg":"最怕山竹名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1aa1409f586768fa1d45a24b36da8b8ff02d20d","tid":1071309,"uid":99856,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T10:58:47.000Z","msg":"呢幾個救護哥仔都有種英氣<br />\n少見少見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"952daee687ddc740762c51d526718c4a59ea5977","tid":1071309,"uid":28765,"like":6,"dislike":0